{"tid":411764,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍芽接線] 大家點睇 Shure RMCE-BT1 MMCX","createTime":"2017-09-24T05:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T11:21:16.000Z","uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4cb59d07c58c3eba4fde835d74bd233fc0be7a","tid":411764,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/135704_05f2a6b46386fe41dda583b7684eac02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F135704_05f2a6b46386fe41dda583b7684eac02.jpg&h=672a57f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對幾家傳統耳機廠商來說，雖然有賴於 iPhone 將耳機市場推向高峰，但現在耳機市場也因為蘋果取消 3.5mm 耳機孔之後陷入不得不改變的情況；身為老早就投入平衡電樞耳機市場的錄音設備老字號 Shure 也在近期積極地推出因應產品，除了日前推出的 Lightning 轉換線，近期則一口氣推出兩款藍牙耳機與藍牙轉換線，包括 SE215 搭配藍牙線的同捆版，以及 SE112 Wireless 無線耳機，與 RMCE-BT1 MMCX 藍牙轉換線，從有線連接轉向無線化。"},{"pid":"40c3f81c5d68d895cca86b7cdb76b960f30392fd","tid":411764,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"啱啱轉用 iPhone 8，要用條勁柒既接駁線先用到舊耳機，所以索性想用藍芽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻仲要包埋 Mic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以心郁郁"},{"pid":"99cb434005ccfcd74fadcd8e87f00d48e457b8e6","tid":411764,"uid":4280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:09:27.000Z","msg":"我本身都想換，但好似話個mic好細聲，你上網睇左先好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ab286dda4f6923dc3dbb456cac4d565d02f1dd","tid":411764,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我本身都想換，但好似話個mic好細聲，你上網睇左先好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵到全部都係宣傳網頁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d645516e638be1a15c6607b07814368697489f7","tid":411764,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike"